title: Vietnam Colony
subTitle: A real estate company appoints Krishnamurthy to vacate a colony, claiming it is filled with anti-social elements. He gradually realises that the company is being unjust to its residents.

title: Chanakya
subTitle: Arjun, a highly sought-after RAW agent, is known for his skills at catching some of the most hardened criminals. However, he falls in danger when he goes after Ibrahim Qureshi, a terrorist.

title: Vetri Malai
subTitle: Jeeva and Madhavi live with their dad and stepmother. Jeeva marries Raja, while Madhavi is visually impaired and has trouble getting married. Madhavi's life takes a turn when she meets Raja's friend.

title: Paarai
subTitle: Durai Raj, a lorry driver, has only one friend, Jayaram. However, when his friend dies, Durai Raj strives to support his family.

title: Vanaja Girija
subTitle: Sisters Vanaja and Girija believe they were abandoned by their father due to the influence of a man named Ramanathan. The duo vow to alienate Ramanathan from his family as he did to theirs.

title: Thambi Vettothi Sundaram
subTitle: Sundaram is brought up in a town where every educated person is involved in some kind of illegal business. However, he refuses to follow the same path and finds solace in the company of Aala.

title: Vesham
subTitle: Circumstances force a famous singer, Ashok, to work at a local music shop, where he meets his fan, Devi. Soon, she decides to approach Ashok to teach Raja, who has misbehaved with her, a lesson.
